trans-unit.source: Represents an attribute of a toolbox item.
The <xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute> class provides a way to specify an attribute for a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>.
In addition to what the <xref:System.Attribute> class provides, this class of object stores the type of the toolbox item.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute"></xref> class and specifies whether to use default initialization values.
By default, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute.ToolboxItemType%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>.
`true` to create a toolbox item attribute for a default type; `false` to associate no default toolbox item support for this attribute.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute"></xref> class using the specified name of the type.

This constructor expects the `toolboxItemTypeName` parameter to be in the form \<*name of the item type*>*,* \<*name of the assembly*> (for example, System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem, System.Drawing.Design).
The names of the type of the toolbox item and of the assembly that contains the type.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute"></xref> class using the specified type of the toolbox item.
The type of the toolbox item.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute"></xref> class and sets the type to the default, <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>.
This field is read-only.
By default, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute.ToolboxItemType%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>.
Returns a value that indicates whether this instance is equal to a specified object.
An <xref href="System.Object"></xref> to compare with this instance or a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
`true` if obj equals the type and value of this instance; otherwise, `false`.
Returns the hash code for this instance.
A 32-bit signed integer hash code.
Gets a value indicating whether the current value of the attribute is the default value for the attribute.
By default, this value returns `false` from the method defined in the <xref:System.Attribute> class.
`true` if the current value of the attribute is the default; otherwise, `false`.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute"></xref> class and sets the type to `null`.
This field is read-only.
Gets or sets the type of the toolbox item.
The type of the toolbox item.
The type cannot be found.
Gets or sets the name of the type of the current <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>.
The fully qualified type name of the current toolbox item.
